{"id":"cmmel06oy0001nriu6n8dxv4j","projectId":"cmmda4tdu00007oqcfk611gwg","campaignId":"cmmekujfn00012ihyp8y1mnei","type":"social_post","subtype":"feed_post","platform":"instagram","title":"Eid Mubarak: Compassionate Care, Every Day","description":null,"status":"IN_REVIEW","currentVersion":1,"metadata":"{\"model\":\"claude-opus-4-6\",\"post_type\":\"celebration\",\"target_audience\":\"All followers\",\"scheduled_time\":\"2026-03-13T18:00:00Z\",\"hashtags\":[\"EidMubarak\",\"RamadanCare\",\"ZavisHealth\",\"PatientFirst\",\"CompassionateCare\"],\"day\":7}","tags":null,"createdAt":"2026-03-06T07:37:08.567Z","updatedAt":"2026-03-06T07:46:33.072Z","versions":[{"id":"cmmel06pa0003nriud3p1y6si","assetId":"cmmel06oy0001nriu6n8dxv4j","version":1,"filePath":null,"content":"Eid Mubarak from the Zavis team.\n\nThis Ramadan, we celebrated healthcare providers who went the extra mile for their patients:\n\nClinics that adjusted their hours for fasting patients.\nPractitioners who asked about fasting before prescribing.\nTeams that shared Ramadan health tips with genuine care.\nPractices that made every patient feel seen and respected.\n\nThe holy month may be ending, but compassionate care never stops.\n\nThank you for putting patients first. Today and every day.\n\nEid Mubarak.\n\n#EidMubarak #RamadanCare #ZavisHealth #PatientFirst #CompassionateCare #HealthcareExcellence #EidAlFitr #Gratitude #HealthTech #PatientEngagement","metadata":"{\"model\":\"claude-opus-4-6\",\"post_type\":\"celebration\",\"target_audience\":\"All followers\",\"scheduled_time\":\"2026-03-13T18:00:00Z\",\"hashtags\":[\"EidMubarak\",\"RamadanCare\",\"ZavisHealth\",\"PatientFirst\",\"CompassionateCare\"],\"day\":7}","changelog":"Initial generation","createdAt":"2026-03-06T07:37:08.590Z","feedbacks":[]}],"brandChecks":[{"id":"cmmelca9800016j98aqw0n4dd","assetId":"cmmel06oy0001nriu6n8dxv4j","versionNumber":1,"checkType":"visual_qa","score":90,"passed":true,"details":"{\"text_legibility\":95,\"brand_consistenc